text: Elisabeth Chevanne Brunel (born 2 December 1975) is a road cyclist from France. She represented her nation at the 1998, 1999 and 2004 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1975 births Category:French female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
